body:
The following query uses fuzzy (`~`) to do a fuzzy search in
the `title` field for movie titles that contain terms similar to
`catch` with up to a two character variation.

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "queryString": {
        "defaultPath": "title",
        "query": "catch~2"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 10
  },
  {
    "$project": {
       "_id": 0,
       "title": 1
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  { title: 'Catch-22' },
  { title: 'Catch That Girl' },
  { title: 'Catch That Kid' },
  { title: 'Catch a Fire' },
  { title: 'Catch Me Daddy' },
  { title: 'Death Watch' },
  { title: 'Patch Adams' },
  { title: "Batch '81" },
  { title: 'Briar Patch' },
  { title: 'Night Watch' }
]
```
